		"components": [],
		"description": "This is a Jira to start the discussion on migrating Alloy to ES6.  Two specific things come to mind that can happen:\r\n\r\n1.  If we don't have a JS runtime that supports ES6 yet, a pre-compiler Alloy plugin using Babel would work.\r\n\r\n2.  Alloy controllers re-written to be ES6 classes (big undertaking, I know)",
		"attachment": [],
		"flagged": false,
		"summary": "Upgrade Alloy to ES6 ",
		"creator": {
			"name": "rblalock",
			"key": "rblalock",
			"displayName": "Rick Blalock",
			"active": false,
			"timeZone": "America/Havana"
		},
